#: ../../C/cretinous.rst:9
msgid ""
"Wrong; stupid; non-functional; very poorly designed. Also used pejoratively "
"of people. See :ref:`dread-high-bit-disease` for an example. Approximate "
"synonyms: :ref:`bletcherous`\\, :ref:`bagbiting`\\, :ref:`losing`\\, "
":ref:`brain-damaged`\\."
msgstr ""
"間違っている。愚かである。機能しない。非常に設計が悪い。人に対して軽蔑的にも使われます。例については\\ :ref:`dread-high-bit-"
"disease`\\ を参照。近い同義語:\\ :ref:`bletcherous`\\ 、\\ :ref:`bagbiting`\\ 、\\ "
":ref:`losing`\\ 、\\ :ref:`brain-damaged`\\ 。"
